				\begin{document}$$h^2 = 0.5$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M124"><mml:mrow><mml:msup><mml:mi>h</mml:mi><mml:mn>2</mml:mn></mml:msup><mml:mo>=</mml:mo><mml:mn>0.5</mml:mn></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2021_4079_Article_IEq54.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula></p></caption><table frame="hsides" rules="groups"><thead><tr><th align="left"/><th align="left">100 causal SNPs, <inline-formula id="IEq55"><alternatives><tex-math id="M125">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
